navmid.graph
Class ObjectNode

java.lang.Object
  navmid.graph.Node
      navmid.graph.ObjectNode
Direct Known Subclasses:
CommandNode, DisplayableNode, ItemNode
public class ObjectNode
extends Node

An Object Node is a node of the graph corresponding to an abstraction of live Java objects. Usually these are the objects allocated at a given program point. Finally an object is identified when it has been recognized by the tracker. This boolean can flip from false to true but never from true to false.

piac6784
